
Overview
========

This puppet module manages grub

Variables
=========


Classes
=======

grub
----

The grub class performs all steps needed to the use of grub such as package
installation


Defines
=======

grub::
----------

Add a rule to the ferm rules.d directory

Variables used :
	$host = false, 
	$table="filter", 
	$chain="INPUT", 
	$rule, 
	$description="", 
	$prio="00", 
	$notarule=false


